      <title>南非国民议会支持征用法案草案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/south-africa-s-national-assembly-backs-draft-expropriation-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党非洲人国民大会的立法者投票支持新起草的立法，该立法将允许政府为了国家利益而无偿征用土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/south-africa-s-national-assembly-backs-draft-expropriation-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:13:15 GMT</pubDate>
