    <item>
      <title>特鲁多承诺提高租房者的权利以争取年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/trudeau-pledges-to-boost-renters-rights-in-bid-for-young-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多宣布了支持租房者权利并帮助他们过渡到拥有住房的措施，因为他的政府试图赢回加拿大年轻人失去的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/trudeau-pledges-to-boost-renters-rights-in-bid-for-young-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国要求盟国加强对中国芯片设备的维修</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/us-is-asking-allies-to-tighten-servicing-of-chip-gear-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登政府寻求进一步挫败北京制造尖端半导体的雄心，美国要求盟友对中国芯片制造设备的维护施加更多限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/us-is-asking-allies-to-tighten-servicing-of-chip-gear-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比利时极右翼民意支持率上升，引发人们对政治瘫痪的新担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/belgian-election-far-right-rise-in-polls-raises-new-fears-of-paralysis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比利时荷兰语地区的一个曾经被边缘化的极右分离主义政党在六月全国大选之前获得了更多主流支持，这可能会让这个分裂国家的治理变得更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/belgian-election-far-right-rise-in-polls-raises-new-fears-of-paralysis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长称意大利目前将保留邮政51%的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/italy-to-retain-51-of-poste-for-now-finance-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利财政部长 Giancarlo Giorgetti 周三表示，意大利政府出售 Poste Italiane SpA 将分阶段进行，国家可能最初保留 51% 的股份，而不是立即将其持股减少到计划的 35%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/italy-to-retain-51-of-poste-for-now-finance-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现金紧张的突尼斯拒绝卡塔尔援助计划，称其面临独立风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/cash-tight-tunisia-snubs-qatari-aid-plan-as-risking-independence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯议会禁止卡塔尔国营基金向这个资金短缺的北非国家扩张，这可能会阻碍其振兴经济和避免违约的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/cash-tight-tunisia-snubs-qatari-aid-plan-as-risking-independence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非商业中心将缺水五年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/johannesburg-water-crisis-no-relief-for-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府官员表示，在 2029 年左右跨境供应扩张完成之前，南非商业中心豪登省将出现缺水情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/johannesburg-water-crisis-no-relief-for-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:23:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯扩大打击范围，乌克兰第二大城市遭制导炸弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/russian-ballistic-missile-hits-ukraine-s-mykolayiv-injures-six</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局表示，东北部城市哈尔科夫遭到制导炸弹袭击，造成至少一人死亡，多人受伤，这是自两年多前战争爆发以来该市首次遭受此类袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/russian-ballistic-missile-hits-ukraine-s-mykolayiv-injures-six</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:17:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平在荷兰总理访问期间抨击技术障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/xi-slams-technological-barriers-during-dutch-premier-s-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在荷兰首相马克·吕特访问北京期间批评了“技术壁垒”，因为美国正在推动加强对ASML Holding NV向亚洲国家销售芯片制造设备的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/xi-slams-technological-barriers-during-dutch-premier-s-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:11:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
